node.text: This week marks @specialocanada’s Global Week of Inclusion. I cannot emphasize how great Special O is enough and I’m so excited to get back to coaching floor #hockey every week. Let’s all #choosetoinclude, always

node.text:
Did I say Ducksworth first?! 🦆👇

Get your own Strawberry Shortcake & Vanilla Cream Puff Dream Donuts, they’re much tastier than pucks and there are no artificial flavours or colours. Click the link in my bio to download the @timhortons app #DroppedInATims #Partner 🍩

node.text:
The biggest beauty of all time. Thanks for everything you did for our team and city Patty, words can’t describe how much we loved you. But with every end comes a new beginning... WELCOME TO WINNIPEG @duber18.
.
Oh- and for the last time... Laine > Matthews 👀
